        <div id='nomineeAccordion'><h3 class=>AR Experience of the Year</h3><div class='nominees'><ul class='nominee-list'><li class='winners'>Winner<br><a href='https://go.playko.com/a320' target='blank'>A320 Cockpit Simulator</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://worldsdemolisher.totalviz.com/' target='blank'>Worlds Demolisher</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://player.8i.com/webxr' target='blank'>Volumetric WebXR Player</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://a.flow.gl/flow/yuqa8d' target='blank'>Texas Blackout</a></li></ul></div><h3 class=>Framework of the Year</h3><div class='nominees'><ul class='nominee-list'><li class='winners'>Winner<br><a href='https://github.com/pmndrs/react-xr' target='blank'>React XR</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://github.com/AR-js-org/AR.js/' target='blank'>AR.js</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://github.com/jbaicoianu/janusweb' target='blank'>JanusWeb</a></li></ul></div><h3 class=>Platform of the Year</h3><div class='nominees'><ul class='nominee-list'><li class='winners'>Winner<br><a href='https://readyplayer.me/' target='blank'>Ready Player Me</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://somniumspace.com/parcel/' target='blank'>Somnium Space Web</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://cybrxr.com/' target='blank'>CYBR</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://dreamwave.tech/' target='blank'>Dreamwave</a></li></ul></div><h3 class=>Event of the Year</h3><div class='nominees'><ul class='nominee-list'><li class='winners'>Winner<br><a href='https://www.secondskyfest.com/' target='blank'>Secret Sky</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='' target='blank'>OnboardXR</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://www.eventbrite.com/e/vr-book-chat-mary-shelley-sci-fi-gothic-stories-and-frankenstein-tickets-167394709081' target='blank'>Mary Shelley</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://fivars.net/' target='blank'>FIVARS</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://www.unwireddancetheatre.com/unwanted-waters-mocap-xr' target='blank'>Unwanted Waters</a></li></ul></div><h3 class=>WebXR Software of the Year</h3><div class='nominees'><ul class='nominee-list'><li class='winners'>Winner<br><a href='https://wonderlandengine.com/' target='blank'>Wonderland Engine</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://brushworkvr.com/paint' target='blank'>Brushwork</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://github.com/Igalia/wolvic' target='blank'>Wolvic Browser</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://github.com/De-Panther/unity-webxr-export' target='blank'>WebXR Export</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://vartiste.xyz/' target='blank'>VARTISTE</a></li></ul></div><h3 class=>R.O.X. Award – Return on Experience</h3><div class='nominees'><ul class='nominee-list'><li class='winners'>Winner<br><a href='https://raw-emotions.phoria.com.au/' target='blank'>RAW Emotion Unites Us</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://readyplayer.me/' target='blank'>Ready Player Me</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://a.flow.gl/flow/kve84xit' target='blank'>BabyTime Analysis</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://wonderlandengine.com/' target='blank'>Wonderland Engine</a></li></ul></div><h3 class=>World of the Year</h3><div class='nominees'><ul class='nominee-list'><li class='winners'>Winner<br><a href='https://hubs.sciencevr.com/' target='blank'>ScienceVR Hubs</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://framevr.io/edumetaverse' target='blank'>EDUmetaverse</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://www.secondskyfest.com/' target='blank'>Secret Sky</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://cybrxr.com/quest' target='blank'>Grace Weber’s Virtual Studio</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://obscura.world/' target='blank'>Obscura</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://vrto.spatialized.events/' target='blank'>VRTO</a></li></ul></div><h3 class=>Game of the Year</h3><div class='nominees'><ul class='nominee-list'><li class='winners'>Winner<br><a href='https://plockle.com/play' target='blank'>Plockle</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='' target='blank'>Archery Dungeon</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://constructarcade.com/game/ski-fit-365/' target='blank'>Ski Fit 365</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://summitscramble.com/' target='blank'>Summit Scramble</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://constructarcade.com/game/santas-workshop/' target='blank'>Santa’s Workshop</a></li></ul></div><h3 class=>WebXR Developer of the Year</h3><div class='nominees'><ul class='nominee-list'><li class='winners'>Winner<br><a href='https://webaverse.com/' target='blank'>Adrian Biedrzycki</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://supercritical.net/' target='blank'>James Baicoianu</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://www.nunustudio.org/' target='blank'>José Ferrão</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='http://www.playko.com' target='blank'>Yinch Yeap</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://de-panther.com/' target='blank'>Oren De-Panther Weizman</a></li></ul></div><h3 class=>Video Experience of the Year</h3><div class='nominees'><ul class='nominee-list'><li class='winners'>Winner<br><a href='https://liquidcinemavr.com/fly/' target='blank'>The Magic Of Flight</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://bit.ly/FIVARS-TheResidents-Inside-a-Circle-of-Dreams' target='blank'>Inside a Circle of Dreams</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://cybrxr.com/quest' target='blank'>Grace Weber’s Virtual Studio</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://fivars.spatialized.events/webxrawards#video-kiosk_a92f6bf724cc6378dfd34c9ef92feff1_17&janus.url=https%3A%2F%2Ffivars.spatialized.events%2Fvideo%2FRukh%3Fbacklink%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ffivars.spatialized.events%252Fwebxrawards' target='blank'>Rukh</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://bit.ly/FIVARS-Katya-Be-Your-Own-Dentist' target='blank'>Be Your Own Dentist</a></li></ul></div><h3 class=>Entertainment Experience of the Year</h3><div class='nominees'><ul class='nominee-list'><li class='winners'>Winner<br><a href='https://manifested.app/' target='blank'>Manifested</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://www.unwireddancetheatre.com/unwanted-waters-mocap-xr' target='blank'>Unwanted Waters</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://cybrxr.com/quest' target='blank'>Grace Weber’s Virtual Studio</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://fivars.spatialized.events/webxrawards#video-kiosk_a92f6bf724cc6378dfd34c9ef92feff1_17&janus.url=https%3A%2F%2Ffivars.spatialized.events%2Fvideo%2FRukh%3Fbacklink%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ffivars.spatialized.events%252Fwebxrawards' target='blank'>Rukh</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://vr.pbs.org/' target='blank'>Virtual Screen on the Green</a></li></ul></div><h3 class=>Creator of the Year</h3><div class='nominees'><ul class='nominee-list'><li class='winners'>Winner<br><a href='https://keramsbookreport.com/index.php/essays-articles-interviews/' target='blank'>Keram Malicki-Sánchez</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://www.dulce.com' target='blank'>Dulce Baerga</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://caitlinkrause.com' target='blank'>Caitlin Krause</a></li></ul></div><h3 class=>Education Experience of the Year</h3><div class='nominees'><ul class='nominee-list'><li class='winners'>Winner<br><a href='https://liquidcinemavr.com/fly/' target='blank'>The Magic Of Flight</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://go.playko.com/a320' target='blank'>A320 Cockpit Simulator</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://mirv.tec.mx/BigBrainTime/cerebro.html' target='blank'>Big Brain Time</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://framevr.io/edumetaverse' target='blank'>EDUmetaverse</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://hubs.sciencevr.com/' target='blank'>ScienceVR Hubs</a></li></ul></div><h3 class=>Experience of the Year</h3><div class='nominees'><ul class='nominee-list'><li class='winners'>Winner<br><a href='https://liquidcinemavr.com/fly/' target='blank'>The Magic Of Flight</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://bit.ly/FIVARS-TheResidents-Inside-a-Circle-of-Dreams' target='blank'>Inside a Circle of Dreams</a></li><li class=''>  <a href='https://raw-emotions.phoria.com.au/' target='blank'>RA